2022-11-03:
	- Changed monophonic voice allocation: When releasing a note while still having others held,
	  the last played note rather than the highest will be played.
	- Changed polyphonic voice allocation: Proper round-robin allocator which prefers released
	  voices over active ones.

2022-11-20:
	- When changing filter configuration, do notturn the volume all down to 0, wait 100ms, turn it up again.
